Subject: CHANGE: DMV variables should local copies to generate events
Date: Mon, 16 Nov 2009 11:43:35 -0700
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

Since DMV variables are not changing continuously, they should be  
updated as discrete integer (or real) variables locally.  These local  
copies should be used in always@ sensitivity lists to determine when  
to generate events.

